{"type": "article", "id": 8805, "title": "拍摄防护罩", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-23T07:17:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235110fMw74xFCbZ2o0sXq.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t最近 Odo Fioravanti 为意大利 TIM 移动公司设计了一款拍摄防护罩，试图满足某些恶劣环境下的拍摄需求。这里的“环境”主要指的是工人的操作环境，最典型的便是焊接。从防护服，头盔到面罩，鞋子，Odo Fioravanti 设计了全面的记录设备。如安全帽上设有夹扣，可以方便工人把手机等拍摄用具放上去进行拍摄，鞋子上设有蓝牙读数器，可以记录劳动中所产生的可用于后期需要的日常数据。方便工人记录工作过程，发现问题，分享体会。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235106CIFEr0qk2g8xmwYp.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235106Q7hR4eBSVPwJ6YsG.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.55867971\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235107od2kCYyaBnJzVAF8.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235107UR63xc1dYCE8ovrO.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.77261614\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052351084jTr0KeDbmvcHY7L.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235108zN4O27uGwH0tMyrX.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.72493888\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235109r9TsSwBiWLPjOJxY.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235109S3LpMKE7zyf2lwst.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235109R71EtoxupOD4FbP6.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.59535452\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}